another way: you need a way to convert the stonk into one or more other ass=
ets that are, fundamentally, uncorrelated, while still convincing the ape a=
rmy that you are doing this all in character. The persona has to have a goo=
d reason to buy this asset, good enough to keep the stonk afloat to arrange=
