redicated in large part on the assumption that this new asset is indeed mor=
e-or-less uncorrelated from the stonk.At the Margins, Ranjan Roy made a rel=
ated argument earlier this week. I think this is an interesting theory but =
I do not fully buy it. For one thing,=C2=A0I think that the value of Musk T=
witter will be very correlated to the value of Tesla stock, at least to the=
