be able to shake his =E2=80=9CTwitter Sitter.=E2=80=9DA judge on Wednesday =
rejected Musk=E2=80=99s request to ditch his 2018 deal with the U.S. Securi=
ties and Exchange Commission that required a company lawyer to screen all h=
is Tesla Inc.-related tweets. The Tesla CEO, who appears to have clinched h=
is bid to buy Twitter, had accused the SEC of harassing him and claimed the=
