e=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;">=09<li =
style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">When it signed the merger agreement on Monday=
, Twitter=E2=80=99s board presumably knew what the earnings release would s=
